Params: {3: 'At the center of the "buildings" with varied exteriors stands a colossal four-winged white raven.'}
{3: 'Stars and planets form iridescent light bands, encircling a dark sun.'}
{3: 'The "city" is filled with starlight, yet remains deathly silent.'}
{3: "Ishmael sits atop the city's tallest buildingâ€”"}
{3: 'This is her favorite spot, where she always brings herself in her free time.'}
{3: 'Only here can she feel... that she is not alone.'}
{3: 'Upon sensing the strange presence of life, Ishmael slightly raises her head, only to immediately furrow her brow in disgust.'}
{3: 'Multiple Hetero-Creatures gradually emerge from the Red Tide seeping through a fissure unseen.'}
{3: 'She draws her Keystaff, coldly observing the vile creatures spawning before her.'}
